name: Beast King Barbaros
desc: You can Normal Summon/Set this card without Tributing, but its original ATK becomes 1900. You can Tribute 3 monsters to Tribute Summon (but not Set) this card. If Summoned this way: Destroy all cards your opponent controls.

str2: Tribute 3 monsters to Tribute Summon this card
